text.tspan: A 19 year old college student. Park'nson was a vocalist in his music
course. At a gig, the drummer decided it'd be a cool effect to add
a tiny bit of gunpowder inside of the bass drum. It'd be a cool way to
end the show blowing off the front skin. They accidentially added too
much, and it ended up blowing Park'nson into a wall covered in drain
pipes. All it took was one kick. Park'nson hit the wall so hard the pipes
impaled him in 3 different places. We found him and took care of him.
but we cant remove the pipes.
